context:
KR:
&lt;color=#84a79d&gt;그것이 네가 나아갈 모험의 조건이다.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#84a79d&gt;That is the condition of your adventure.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#84a79d&gt;이를 받아들일 마음이 있다면, 너의 이름을 내게 말해라.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#84a79d&gt;If you are willing to accept these terms, then speak your name to me.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;이게 다음 구역으로 갈 수 있는 장치인가봐…&gt;
EN:
&lt;So this is the 'device' that leads us to our next destination, huh...&gt;

KR:
&lt;버튼을 누르면 우리가 이 구역에서 할 일은 끝난 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;So... we press this button, and our job's done here?&gt;

KR:
&lt;돈키호테, 너를 팔아넘기려고 했어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don Quixote, he was trying to sell you out.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…재밌었으면 놔줬을 거라는 이야기?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... So you would've just let him do his thing if it was... interesting?&gt;
